    | Data          { [$1] }
    | DataSig       { [$1] }  -- lone data type signature in mutual block
    | Record        { [$1] }
    | RecordSig     { [$1] }  -- lone record signature in mutual block
    | Infix         { [$1] }
    | Generalize    {  $1  }
    | Mutual        { [$1] }
    | Abstract      { [$1] }
    | Private       { [$1] }
    | Instance      { [$1] }
    | Macro         { [$1] }
    | Postulate     { [$1] }
    | Primitive     { [$1] }
    | Open          {  $1  }
--    | Import      { [$1] }
    | ModuleMacro   { [$1] }
    | Module        { [$1] }
    | Pragma        { [$1] }
    | Syntax        { [$1] }
    | PatternSyn    { [$1] }
